title: Hallmark-Window Wonderland [2013]
description:
Hallmark-Window Wonderland [2013]

Air Date: 23 Nov 2013

Summary: WINDOW WONDERLAND is about a rival male and female decorators who are determined to outshine each other by competing to create the best Christmas display at a famous New York City Department Store. In their attempts to outdo each other, their windows get progressively out-of-control, culminating in disaster, until they remember the real meaning of Christmas and find love and themselves in the process.
